2.12:
Wisdom will save you
    from the way of evil,
        from the person who speaks devious things,

2.16:
Wisdom will also save you
    from an adulterous woman,
        from a loose woman with her smooth talk,

8.23:
I was appointed from everlasting
    from the first,
        before the earth began.

23.15:
My son,
    if you have a wise heart,
        my heart will rejoice as well.
